org.jmisb.api.klv.st0806.poiaoi

Class RvtPoiAoiTextString

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jmisb.api.klv.st0806.poiaoi.RvtPoiAoiTextString
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IKlvValue, IRvtPoiAoiMetadataValue

    public class RvtPoiAoiTextString
extends Object
implements IRvtPoiAoiMetadataValue
    Represents a string value in ST 0806 RVT POI or AOI Local Set.

    These should use the ASCII (strictly, ISO-7) subset of UTF-8.
